## ⛳ Completion signal — REQUIRED LAST LINE (run_claude_job.sh reads this for Steve's Telegram alert)

After all work and logging, the VERY LAST line of your output MUST be exactly one of:
- `ROUTINE_COMPLETE` — the canon-reviewer ran in deep-sweep mode AND drafted the proposals that cleared the bar (≥1 now surfaced, OR correctly zero). A coherent-canon result IS complete.
- `ROUTINE_INCOMPLETE: <one-line reason>` — the canon-reviewer could not read the corpus (blocked-*), the --list enumeration failed, or the Telegram push failed when proposals existed.

Output nothing after that line.
